## Startup Performance (Activity Displayed)

- Before Startup Tracing:

```
ActivityManager: Displayed com.companyname.yourapp/MainActivity: +0s0ms
```

- After Startup Tracing:

```
ActivityManager: Displayed com.companyname.yourapp/MainActivity: +0s0ms
```
